      "description": "Amplify ETF Trust - Amplify S&P 500 Dividend Drivers ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by Amplify Investments LLC. The fund is co-managed by Tidal Investments LLC. The fund invests in public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in growth and value stocks of large-cap companies. The fund invests in dividend paying stocks of companies within the market capitalization range of the S&P 500 Index. It seeks to track the performance of the S&P 500 Dividend Drivers Index, by using full replication technique. Amplify ETF Trust - Amplify S&P 500 Dividend Drivers ETF is domiciled in the United States.",
